  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. The equation <math><mn>14</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>14</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>52</mn></math> gives <math><mn>28</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>52</mn></math>. Subtracting 28 yields <math><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>24</mn></math>.</p><p>Choices A, B, and C are incorrect; they correspond to incorrect perimeters.</p>",
